{"2239990": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Love n Dream 3", "steam_appid": 2239990, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239990/extras/4fc655fb4a874f78475b7ddbc872cdf9.poster.avif?t=1746917110\" width=382 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239990/extras/4fc655fb4a874f78475b7ddbc872cdf9.webm?t=1746917110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239990/extras/4fc655fb4a874f78475b7ddbc872cdf9.mp4?t=1746917110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事背景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《爱与梦3》邀請你化身為大衛，踏上前往神秘澤尼赫城的迷人旅程。這是一款沉浸式角色扮演冒險遊戲，結合了探索、解謎和角色養成，帶來獨一無二的體驗。與環境互動，解決各種挑戰和謎題，提升大衛的才能與特長，這些都會在你的約會之旅中發揮至關重要的作用。[/p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5位獨特而迷人的女孩：</strong> 每個角色都有不同的個性、喜好和背景。你將體驗她們的故事、生活等等，並與角色展開多元的互動。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239990/extras/e356a603ada41651dee2606a439e7e46.avif?t=1746917110\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>中世紀與科幻世界的融合：</strong> 探索一個古老與未來完美交織的獨特宇宙，體驗雙重世界的魅力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>策略性三消解謎：</strong> 在獨特的三消謎題中做出正確決策，優化你的約會體驗，深化彼此關係。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239990/extras/b303916abf5b3f1d7d318013ea4f8648.poster.avif?t=1746917110\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239990/extras/b303916abf5b3f1d7d318013ea4f8648.webm?t=1746917110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239990/extras/b303916abf5b3f1d7d318013ea4f8648.mp4?t=1746917110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有趣的小遊戲：</strong> 參與各種小遊戲，包括健身、射擊場、釣魚以及種植魔法草藥等活動。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>購物與禮物：</strong> 在城市的各個地點探索，為你遇到的可愛女孩購買物品和禮物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239990/extras/a65d4a9653502349fb59e92703a6257c.poster.avif?t=1746917110\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239990/extras/a65d4a9653502349fb59e92703a6257c.webm?t=1746917110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239990/extras/a65d4a9653502349fb59e92703a6257c.mp4?t=1746917110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>驚豔的視覺效果：</strong> 欣賞融合了亞洲與西方風格的精美背景和藝術作品，帶來視覺盛宴。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>放鬆的音樂：</strong> 在遊戲中悠閒舒緩的音樂中，盡情探索與互動。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>迎接挑戰：</strong> 克服障礙，享受一個充實的約會體驗，同時探索澤尼赫城的複雜之美。</p></li></ul></strong></p>", "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239990/extras/4fc655fb4a874f78475b7ddbc872cdf9.poster.avif?t=1746917110\" width=382 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239990/extras/4fc655fb4a874f78475b7ddbc872cdf9.webm?t=1746917110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239990/extras/4fc655fb4a874f78475b7ddbc872cdf9.mp4?t=1746917110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事背景</h2>